title: Moneyline Monaco - NFL Week 8 Bets: 49ers-Rams, Giants-Seahawks, Russell Wilson & Broncos vs Jaguars
itunes:title: Moneyline Monaco - NFL Week 8 Bets: 49ers-Rams, Giants-Seahawks, Russell Wilson & Broncos vs Jaguars
description:
Alex Monaco shares his sports betting insight and gives you his final bets heading into Week 8 of the NFL season starting with Russell Wilson returning as the Broncos take on Trevor Lawrence and the Jaguars in London, Jimmy Garoppolo and the 49ers vs Matthew Stafford and the Rams, Saquon Barkley and the Giants taking on Geno Smith and the Seahawks, and much more! #Volume #Herd #ColinCowherd
